"{\"uid\": \"news.cgtn.com-news-2024-05-04-China-s-small-commodities-hub-Yiwu-abuzz-as-Paris-Olympic-nears-1tkHj3tMmju-p.html\", \"text\": \"Our Privacy Statement & Cookie Policy  By continuing to browse our site you agree to our use of cookies, revised Privacy Policy and Terms of Use. You can change your cookie settings through your browser.  Copied  With less than three months to go for the 2024 Paris Olympics, the biggest sporting event of the year is also generating rising demand for Olympic-themed products \\u00e2\\u0080\\u0093 many of them produced in east China\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s Yiwu City. CGTN's Wu Bin visited the \\\"capital of small commodities\\\" to find out more.  SITEMAP  EXPLORE MORE  DOWNLOAD OUR APP  Copyright \\u00c2\\u00a9 2024 CGTN.\\u00e4\\u00ba\\u00acICP\\u00e5\\u00a4\\u008720000184\\u00e5\\u008f\\u00b7  Disinformation report hotline: 010-85061466  SITEMAP  EXPLORE MORE  DOWNLOAD OUR APP  Copyright \\u00c2\\u00a9 2024 CGTN.\\u00e4\\u00ba\\u00acICP\\u00e5\\u00a4\\u008720000184\\u00e5\\u008f\\u00b7  Disinformation report hotline: 010-85061466\"}"